* Single-core 832MHz ARMv6 CPU

=== Downstream status ===

The only device that seems to work with this chipset is the [[Samsung Galaxy Ace i]], although it has not been merged into pmaports. The [[Samsung Galaxy Y]] does not boot.

=== Mainline status ===

No dts in mainline, and there doesn't seem to be any similar chip supported.

